<td valign="top">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td style=" vertical-align: top;">
<a href="http://en.blog.wordpress.com/author/apeatling/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" title="http://en.blog.wordpress.com/author/apeatling/" target="_blank"></a>
